00:13:09.240 --> 00:13:10.220
Explain this to me.

00:13:10.220 --> 00:13:11.600
Sid: What do you mean He's pushing you down?

00:13:11.600 --> 00:13:14.600
Don: Well he's praying for me and I'm starting
to be slain, or -

00:13:14.600 --> 00:13:17.520
Sid: The Spirit of God is putting you down
on the floor; is that what you're saying?

00:13:17.520 --> 00:13:18.020
