thing either works or it doesn't.

00:23:12.240 --> 00:23:13.280
And so now I'm in faith.

00:23:13.280 --> 00:23:14.340
Okay God, what are you going to do?

00:23:14.340 --> 00:23:15.120
What are you going to do?

00:23:15.120 --> 00:23:18.140
And he has me go down to the hamburger place.

00:23:18.140 --> 00:23:23.180
I was challenged three times by unbelief that
nothing was ever going to happen.

00:23:23.180 --> 00:23:31.539
And finally the presence of God actually multiplied
my four dollars back, and I actually bought

00:23:31.539 --> 00:23:32.539
the cheeseburger, coke and fries.

00:23:32.539 --> 00:23:36.990
Sid: Let me just tell you the interesting
